"Both :ref:`collision_layer "
"<class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_layer>` and :ref:`collision_mask "
"<class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_mask>`. Returns "
":ref:`collision_layer <class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_layer>` "
"when accessed. Updates :ref:`collision_layer "
"<class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_layer>` and :ref:`collision_mask "
"<class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_mask>` when modified."
msgstr ""
":ref:`collision_layer <class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_layer>` 和 "
":ref:`collision_mask <class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_mask>` "
"两者。访问时，返回 :ref:`collision_layer "
"<class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_layer>`。修改时，更新 "
":ref:`collision_layer <class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_layer>` 和 "
":ref:`collision_mask <class_PhysicsBody2D_property_collision_mask>`。"

